snippet.title: Ash of Legends Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Ash of Legends is an upcoming, made for VR, first-person-shooter, base-building, tower defense, action-strategy game. This major update includes the new DNA feature, manual reload, anti-gravity launcher, target strong, overcharge, and more!!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1280290?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=web
Discord: https://discord.gg/qybVG2PakT
Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@biofusionvr
